caption.p: Recombinant events in the DENV2 strains. Phylogenetic analysis of DENV type 2 strains based on nucleotide positions (1 to 8891 and 9279 to 10,179) ( a) and (8892 to 9278) ( b) by the maximum likelihood method. Potential recombinant (MF156242), major parent (43254), and minor parent (M29095) were indicated as black circles
